ğŸŒ¸ About the project

Herb App is my ongoing project â€” a bilingual (Finnish & English) phone app that helps people recognize herbs, plants, and berries found in nature.
Itâ€™s meant to be a calm, informative, and beautiful tool for anyone curious about natural remedies, edible wild plants, and plant safety.

Youâ€™ll be able to:

> Identify herbs and plants by name or image
